This module allows to sync picking cost prices with purchase order line
price when moves are already done.

Can be used with product_cost_price_avco_sync.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Known issues / Roadmap
======================

- Remove ``unit_cost`` calculation for stock valuation layer from stock
  moves because this model has been replaced by ``stock.move``.

Bug Tracker
